OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FEnergy giant's move to axe 
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25FWelsh bills 'insulting'    
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, Ovo Energy has been accused of         
OL,6, "degrading" Welsh after axing services 
OL,7, in the language.                       
OL,9,FThe energy company said people could   
OL,10,Finstead use online translation tools to
OL,11,Fread their bills.                      
OL,13,FWelsh language campaign group          
OL,14,FCymdeithas yr Iaith called the move    
OL,15,F"insulting", while the Welsh language  
OL,16,Fcommissioner said she planned to       
OL,17,Fcontact the business.                  
OL,19,FOvo said its Welsh services were only  
OL,20,Fused by a small number of customers.   
